  <條文>
    <條號>Article 13</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[（Deleted）
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 14</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The planning, compilation and the final accounting related to the budget of the Fund and the preparation of the Final Financial Statements thereof, shall be governed by the regulations of the Budget Act, Accounting Act, Final Financial Statements Act, Audit Act and all other related regulations and directions.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 15</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Committee shall promulgate its own accounting system regulating the conduct of the accounting affairs of the Fund in accordance with the laws and regulations.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 16</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Should there be surplus resulting from the execution of the yearly budget of the Fund after the final accounting, the surplus shall be distributed in accordance with the related regulations.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 17</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[At the time the Fund is terminated, a final balance shall be settled; any and all the residuals shall be turned over to the National Treasury.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 18</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The regulations came into effect upon promulgation, with the exception of the amendment to the article, which was amended and promulgated on April 29, 2010 and have been effective since January 1, 2010. And the exception of the amendment to the article, which was amended and promulgated on December 9, 2010 and have been effective since January 1, 2011. And the exception of the amendment to the articles three to five and article nine, which were amended and promulgated on January 20, 2014, and have been effective since January 1, 2014.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
